CM_ BO_ 689 "HVAC FAN SPEED / TEMP BLEND DOORS (READ-ONLY)  $xx8F????7F – 01-07 HVAC fan speed $??8F????7F – constant \"8F\" $??8Fxx??7F – driver HVAC temp blend door $??8F??xx7F – passgr HVAC temp blend door $??8F????7F – constant \"7F\"  Values are actual position, not desired position. They change as driver and passenger heat levels increased/decreased. Signed byte. $80=COOL, $E4=HOT. NOTE: the listed \"constants\" may temporarily change while vehicle initializes.";
