CM_ BO_ 856 "COMPASS HEADING “A”  $?x -- compass heading  0=n 1=ne 2=e 3=se 4=s 5=se 6=w 7=nw f=offline   note: compass was slow on a 2020 5” uConnect radio, fast on a 2021 8.4” uConnect radio, and not present on a 2018 7\" uConnect radio.";
